# Hero: global session picker — wide boat banner + fzf list + cycle navigation.
Output ../assets/demo-picker.gif
Output build/demo-picker.txt
Set Width 1200
Set Height 640
Hide
Type "export PS1='$ '"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show
Type "ferry"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
Down
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 600ms
Up
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 800ms
Escape
Sleep 1s
